{
  "text": "We say that the adversary wins if and only if e = e * . Our commutative encryption scheme is chosen plaintext key recovery resistant if the discrete logarithm problem is hard. (See [CITATION_1] for more discussion.)",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "28892462"
